Network & System:
- network_scan: Capture network packets and show traffic summary
- process_check: List running processes and active network connections  
- firewall_status: Check firewalld/iptables rules and state
- rootkit_scan: Run rkhunter rootkit detection (takes ~2 min)
- usb_devices: List connected USB devices and USBGuard policy
